ygData.subject: Re: North Ro and Freeport
ygData.msgSnippet: Duh Grukk not git to be great Troll basher by trustin everybody dat me talks to. ... Me tinks yous got some kind exterior motif goin on here. You no lie to
ygData.messageBody:
Duh
Grukk not git to be great Troll basher by trustin everybody dat me talks to.
:-)
Me tinks yous got some kind exterior motif goin on here.
You no lie to Grukk!!
Yous does, doesn't ya?
Grukklukk

-----Original Message-----
From: James Schuldes [mailto:jgs@...]
Sent: Monday, May 17, 1999 1:19 PM
To: 'warriors_eq@onelist.com'
Subject: Re: [warriors_eq] North Ro and Freeport


From: James Schuldes <jgs@...>

Hail Grukk!

You look like a smart fellow - big and strong too! Tell ya what - I can get
you that combine weapon you been dreaming of! Here's the deal - my sister
married one of them gypsies and I can get a good price. In fact, they may
not even sell to you - they are kinda funny that way. Just give me 100 plat
and I will get one for you. And I guarantee results! In fact if I can't
get one - don't worry - I will refund 50 plat so you will not lose all of
your plat in the deal. How's that sound to you?

Snyak.

-----Original Message-----
From: Sean.Clark@... [mailto:Sean.Clark@...]
Sent: Monday, May 17, 1999 2:11 PM
To: warriors_eq@onelist.com
Subject: Re: [warriors_eq] North Ro and Freeport

From: Sean.Clark@...

Grukk no need magic weapon to bash dem skeletons.
The only thing Gruk found yet (lvl 12) dat Grukk can't hit
with me Shiny
sword (Fine Steel Longsword - rocks!!) is da elementals in
Lavastorm (don't
try and go there if you aren't an "Evil" race...the Guard
will kill ya!).
Grukk hears them combine weapons are EXPENSIVE! Me hear 120
PP fer the 2
Handed Sword...anybody have info on prices fer Combine
Longsword or
Scimitar?
Any Trolls or Ogres had any experience buyin from them
Gypsies?
Grukklukk da Basher, Bristlebane

-----Original Message-----
From: Patricia Halas [mailto:patty_halas@...]
Sent: Monday, May 17, 1999 1:04 PM
To: warriors_eq@onelist.com
Subject: [warriors_eq] North Ro and Freeport


From: "Patricia Halas" <patty_halas@...>

I am going back to North Ro now that I have finally
reached the 12th Rank

of Barbarian Warrior. Hopefully soon I will have enougth
plat to afford my
dream weapon of a combine long sword (I have 10 plat now).
Any good suggestions for hunting in and around Freeport?
Didn't like
befallen to much since I don't have a magic weapon yet.
Kind of a bummer
when you have to run from a skel that cons blue since I
can't hit him.
Haven't been down to see Troll Town yet. Wonder if it is
worth the trip?

For the Honor and Glory of Rellos Zek;

Patty of Halas
